{"word":"G3543 - νομίζω - nomízō - nom-id'-zo - Suppose","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νομίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">nomízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">nom-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Suppose</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எண்ணிக்கொள், நினை, எண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"1. to hold by custom or usage"},{"paragraph":"2. to deem, think, suppose"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3551 - νόμος - nómos - nom'-os/3551\">G3551</a>; properly to <i>do</i> by <i>law</i> (<i>usage</i>), that is, to <i>accustom</i> (passively <i>be usual</i>); by extension to <i>deem</i> or <i>regard:</i> - suppose, think, be wont.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}